                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 365.117/135.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Ambassador <persName type="from">Page</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Rome</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-08-24">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 24, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>383. Referring Department’s 282, July 12. Foreign Office reports today Da Prato
                    has been released.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Nelson Page.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
